<br>
Hearing her daddy saying how badly it sucks to be stuck doing work you are too smart for because of piss poor choices I made as a younger man has likely done a hell of a lot more as a deterrent than anything else I could ever say.<br>
<br>
I'm very strict, but also very fair and we talk about anything and everything.  Some kids turn out well without that, I never had it and it's no small miracle that I survived the sheer stupidity of much that I did in my past.<br>
<br>
My daughter is 11, we've had the sex talk, the birth control talk, the STD talk, the self defense and when is it ok talk.  Her mom sends her to me for all that stuff because I don't freak out and I listen.<br>
<br>
I know what goes on at my daughter's playground, that's a huge deal.  She knows that even if I do not think she is ready that she can come to me and ask me to get her condoms and I will without me being a dick (no pun intended) about it.  I'd much rather have her not catch any STD or end up pregnant at an early age.  I did not wait until marriage, I don't imagine she will either.<br>
<br>
It's so much harder being a parent in today's world than I ever possibly could have imagined, it's also the most worthwhile thing I've ever been a part of.  That's why crap like what this 12 year old pulled pisses me off so badly.  I know from my own experiences that her parents could not possibly really know their child or what goes on in her life.<br>
<br>
That's just sad. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:century gothic;font-size:small;">Here's to you and here's to me, and if ever we should disagree .... then fuck you, here's to me.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=860.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=860.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=860.topic&start=61&stop=61>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=860.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=860.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=860.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=860.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.threadControl?topicID=860.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=860.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click 